desc: The Wabi Sabi Shop brings Japanese philosophy to your home through products with functional design, high quality, and craftsmanship. Discover beautifully crafted houseware items from Japan. Enjoy worldwide shipping delivered to you from Japan.

layout.text: Tsubame Sanjo: The City of Metalworking
Tsubame Sanjo produces the highest-quality kitchenwares using superior metalworking techniques developed since the Edo period.
